    <item>
      <title>爱迪生首席执行官谈加州野火和诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/edison-ceo-on-california-wildfires-lawsuit-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱迪生国际公司总裁兼首席执行官佩德罗·皮萨罗表示，在火灾发生前，洛杉矶伊顿野火起火点附近的一组输电配电线路“断电”。他还表示，火灾发生前没有任何电气异常迹象。一起诉讼将伊顿野火归咎于能源供应商的设备。皮萨罗在“彭博收盘”节目中谈到了加强系统和重建。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/edison-ceo-on-california-wildfires-lawsuit-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 21:59:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱迪生称洛杉矶伊顿火灾附近线路未发现问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/edison-says-it-found-no-issues-on-lines-near-eaton-fire-in-la</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱迪生国际公司首席执行官佩德罗·皮萨罗表示，该公司没有检测到洛杉矶地区伊顿致命火灾起火点附近的输电线路上有任何电气问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/edison-says-it-found-no-issues-on-lines-near-eaton-fire-in-la</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 21:56:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管存在经济衰退延长的风险，新西兰企业仍保持乐观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/new-zealand-firms-more-upbeat-despite-risk-of-extended-recession</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰经济研究所的数据显示，尽管 2024 年最后一个季度利润放缓、贸易仍然疲软，但新西兰企业对经济前景更为乐观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/new-zealand-firms-more-upbeat-despite-risk-of-extended-recession</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 21:52:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Snowflake 的免费 AI 培训投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/snowflake-s-free-ai-training-investment-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Snowflake 首席执行官 Sridhar Ramaswamy 宣布了一项新的 AI“技能提升”计划，旨在解决全球技能短缺问题。他与 Caroline Hyde 一起在“彭博科技”节目中进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/snowflake-s-free-ai-training-investment-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 21:49:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 可能遭禁，言论自由成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/tiktok-s-possible-ban-puts-free-speech-in-focus-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最高法院正在考虑 TikTok 的撤资或禁令案，卡托研究所的詹妮弗·赫德尔斯顿表示，潜在结果可能会对其他社交媒体平台产生持久影响。她与卡罗琳·海德和迈克·谢泼德一起在《彭博科技》节目中进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/tiktok-s-possible-ban-puts-free-speech-in-focus-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 21:40:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Robinhood 将支付 4500 万美元以解决 SEC 索赔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/robinhood-to-pay-45-million-to-settle-sec-claims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国证券交易委员会周一表示，Robinhood Securities LLC 和 Robinhood Financial LLC 同意支付 4500 万美元的民事罚款，以解决该委员会的一系列指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/robinhood-to-pay-45-million-to-settle-sec-claims</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 21:39:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
